        public static float compare(java.util.ArrayList<Element> E1,
                            java.util.ArrayList<Element> E2,
                            Element parent1,
                            Element parent2,
                            java.lang.String role,
                            java.util.ArrayList<Match> matches)
        This function is applicable on two set of elements having the same role. It permits to identify the matched pairs of elements and return a value between 0 and 1, which corresponds to the similarity degree between them.
        Parameters:

        E2: - second set of elements
        parent1: - the parent element of E1
        parent2: - the parent element of E2
        role: - the role of E1 and E2.
        matches: - the set of matches identified between the elements of E1 and those of E2
